{"type": "article", "id": 41628, "title": "Vetements 退出时装周，以及，明星设计师 Tom Dixon 在香港开店 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-06-05T03:10:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2884, "name": "Diesel"}, {"id": 3313, "name": "洛杉矶"}, {"id": 8845, "name": "摄影展"}, {"id": 35805, "name": "le coq sportif"}, {"id": 41142, "name": "娇兰"}, {"id": 15610, "name": "Chaumet"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 35943, "name": "加拿大鹅"}, {"id": 8926, "name": "Tom Dixon"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170605095800g6baekMWYf42BlEI.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.harpersbazaar.co.uk/fashion/fashion-news/news/a41857/vetements-quits-catwalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Vetements 要退出时装周</strong></a> | 品牌创始人 Demna Gvasalia 表示，已经厌倦了时装周的形式，同时为了节省成本。接下来的 2018 春夏系列会以 showroom 形式展示。另外，近年来火爆的超大廓形卫衣也不会再出现在 Vetements 系列中了。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/jewelry/chaumet-canada-opening-mansvelt-10900082/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>法国高端珠宝品牌 Chaumet 将于今年进军北美市场，首选加拿大而不是美国</strong></a> | Chaumet 的 CEO Jean-Marc Mansvelt 说， 美国是个大国，但在这里扎根很困难，而加拿大更容易接受法国品牌。Chaumet 创始于 1980 年，现属于 LVMH 奢侈品集团，相比集团其它品牌更为低调。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/canada-goose-shares-rose-after-q4-report-10900108/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>加拿大鹅发布上市后的首个财报</strong></a> | 截止至 3 月 31 日的这个季度，加拿大鹅 Canada Goose 集团因上市净亏损 2070 万美元，收入增长了 21.9% 至 4550 万美元。品牌 CEO Dani Reiss 在财报中透露，加拿大鹅的两家旗舰店表现都远超预期。由于直接面向消费者的渠道毛利两倍的增长，使得品牌的整体毛利率提升至了 54.4%。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-06-02/lecoq-guerlain/\" rel=\"nofollow\">娇兰和 Le coq Sportif 联手，发售了一个带有香气的鞋子系列</a>。该系列以经典鞋型 ARTHUR ASHE 为原型，加入了编织工艺，将于 6 月 7 日开始正式在东京新宿的伊势丹及原宿、丸之内 Le coq Sportif 店内发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051016103koGj0phP9JI2V8T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101616uownY5yTKObHe1Zk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101627wljNE7RqOmXorvSI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101633GuhO3E02YUrfaIHZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051016270j3CtExqlJbaIuU2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101633jB6CJt20fzETqmeH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/patchwork-gucci-leather-goods\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessandro Michele 为 Gucci 的经典 Monogram 皮制品带来了更多有趣的产品</a>，比如以 UFO 和星球图案为主的手工缝制刺绣徽章，复古感十足。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101503ERhyD0dZr1FMzHw5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101450G7atycPf654x0eVs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051014494ynHUmfwDZoAWBj1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101450cY0TaBj7bRwypVk5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101457M1DRGaVlbiO8NUxT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051014501kJxwa0UFSKANo2Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101450YLFR46WXqydsJe5t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101503lPrV1TNiwMHA29FL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101451WM0wixvoDhg2jqFd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101457oji6ecY4fwvDMpxt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101450Ei96Oov1mjlFy3V2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101451WoaCygS5mF1KAqM6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101457g54GitzAJKcrqfv8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>明星设计师&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/tom-dixon-open-first-flagship-store-in-south-east-asia\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tom Dixon 在香港开设亚洲首家旗舰店</a>。其中一层是 Tom Dixon 系列全新设计的家具、灯饰及饰物配件，还有一楼则为咖啡室，并由 Nodi 营运，提供一系列手工咖啡及小食。Tom Dixon 说，这个两层楼高的商店，是其亚洲业务扩张的重要里程碑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051014145T9Dapk72u6rX1f4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051014148KuvUSD4ZxIjfzdW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017060510141470618StwIjh9sGgC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101415kr9x8zuUsCSWfZMY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101415NljUSJ4o8fAHLt9z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101415kAzer35KN4Bh0Soq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101426w1GtvU67WcmlR9bI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605101426ETULfkdC83iJPDVh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>位于东京涩谷 Diesel 店地下一楼的 Diesel art Gallery，正在举办以南非为活动中心的两位摄影师 Roger Ballen 与 Asger Carlsen 的联名摄影展<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/no-joke-diesel-art-gallery\" rel=\"nofollow\">「NO JOKE」</a>。展览精选了 25 幅作品，Roger Ballen 擅长在黑白照片上用拼贴、手写涂鸦等方式进行二次创作，而 Roger Ballen 则致力于从“弱者”角度诠释作品，首次合作的二人带来的这 25 幅作品尽管有些奇怪，也散发出某种特殊的迷人气质。 </p><p>展览将持续至 8 月 17 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104119IpGy4UnlBuMAhJba.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104057fl21HPE5pvL8h6N4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706051040574UeWCm9DNhLlKaBy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104056hS5oruC9sUvmYyO7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104056j3Tk4UylZh6MQdsS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104057G9wexd7jL2IiJN1S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.438000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104058UDT48YRaA0gzEsBb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104058DimXjaGbMlBvFd0O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104058ql7kzVecuG1tvdZD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104059UxIVZh4Yo1bwugXO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>喜欢简约又不失质感的设计，洛杉矶新兴品牌<a href=\"https://theloeil.com/collections/new-arrivals/products/elsie-pant-white\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Loeil </a>还不错。Loeil 囊括了衣服、鞋履以及配饰等一系列单品，以简单的单色调为主，价格多在数百美元上下。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104210AJtSOh4Zsu6qPgxD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498780\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104210iKIAr4c5tNlvw0R9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104208WIuMcl0jFxbSLe3E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104208GUOMrCJlaYWpXjZ7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104208PA34nzrwU9vMXyg8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104208XRzYuybeKsScwvVa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104208pf8x0KLGay6zNruE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104436iMLdptGYoewVfFa5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104435l3PivK4ICFXx1DWa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104209luhGo5cyJZQx4v1P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104311J9UyvqP8iIuDhCVl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104209ybhYd3RIKt0aNVQM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104210lfOZ1hNbr3gxGCs0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104209tUGTlEQjiL4qoH5r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104209IQlgJFjnBMsTN2AX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104345AlMnPZCiwBRjYoEa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104522tB8Uw3HEPDJ4qjxs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104526so0Hvwg1rIGzNMTX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104526dpA75kHUQ3riL8Gy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605104552xrW5OpJ7y4QXvwfN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/tom-dixon-open-first-flagship-store-in-south-east-asia\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}